            "id": "https://owenyk.github.io/2021/06/06/Debian%20%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%20nginx%E5%8F%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEwebdav/",
            "url": "https://owenyk.github.io/2021/06/06/Debian%20%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%20nginx%E5%8F%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEwebdav/",
            "title": "Debian 环境安装新版 nginx及配置webdav",
            "date_published": "2021-06-06T01:14:58.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"Debian-环境安装新版-nginx及配置webdav\"><a href=\"#Debian-环境安装新版-nginx及配置webdav\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Debian 环境安装新版 nginx及配置webdav\"></a>Debian 环境安装新版 nginx及配置webdav</h1><h2 id=\"一、Nginx用源安装最新稳定版\"><a href=\"#一、Nginx用源安装最新稳定版\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、Nginx用源安装最新稳定版\"></a>一、Nginx用源安装最新稳定版</h2><h2 id=\"二、源码编译安装最新稳定版：\"><a href=\"#二、源码编译安装最新稳定版：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、源码编译安装最新稳定版：\"></a>二、源码编译安装最新稳定版：</h2><h2 id=\"三、配置webdav模块\"><a href=\"#三、配置webdav模块\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、配置webdav模块\"></a>三、配置webdav模块</h2><p> （1）配置webdav<br> （2）设置webdav帐号和密码：<br> （3）挂载到坚果云方法<br> （4）nginx加入到systemctl服务运行<br> （5）常用命令</p>\n<h2 id=\"四、手机用的连接为webdav软件：\"><a href=\"#四、手机用的连接为webdav软件：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、手机用的连接为webdav软件：\"></a>四、手机用的连接为webdav软件：</h2><h2 id=\"五、一些问题及解决方法\"><a href=\"#五、一些问题及解决方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、一些问题及解决方法\"></a>五、一些问题及解决方法</h2><h2 id=\"一、Nginx用源安装最新稳定版-1\"><a href=\"#一、Nginx用源安装最新稳定版-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、Nginx用源安装最新稳定版\"></a>一、Nginx用源安装最新稳定版</h2><p>参见文章：<a href=\"https://debian.cn/articles/466?www\">Debian 环境安装新版 nginx :</a><br>在 <code>Debian</code> 系统中，我们可以通过 <code>apt-get</code> 安装系统自带的 <code>nginx</code>，这样安装的 <code>nginx</code> 版本略旧。<code>Nginx</code> 官网提供了一些编辑绎好的 <code>deb</code> 安装包，我们只需更新安装源，就可以通过 <code>apt-get</code> 来安装最新的稳定版 <code>Nginx</code>了。</p>\n<p>加载安装源并导入key<br><figure class=\"highlight awk\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs awk\">$ echo deb http:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">//</span>nginx.org<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/packages/</span>debian<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/ stretch nginx | sudo tee /</span>etc<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/apt/</span>sources.list.d/nginx.list <br>$ wget http:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">//</span>nginx.org<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/keys/</span>nginx_signing.key &amp;&amp; sudo apt-key add nginx_signing.key <br>$ sudo apt update &amp;&amp; apt install nginx -y <br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><br>到这一部分就完成了最新稳定版的 <code>Nginx</code> 的安装。</p>\n<p><em>需要注意的是，这一步安装的 Nginx 和系统自带的 nginx 的配置目录略有区别，可以用一下几个简单的命令修正</em>：<br><figure class=\"highlight awk\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs awk\">sudo mkdir <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/&#123;sites-available,sites-enabled&#125;<br>sudo mv <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/conf.d/</span>* <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/sites-available<br>sudo rmdir -f <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/conf.d/</span><br>sudo perl -pi -e <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;s/conf.d/sites-enabled/g&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/nginx.conf<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>其他问题：<br><code>bash: nginx：未找到命令</code><br>由于shell命令基本都在<code>/usr/bin</code>，<code>/usr/sbin</code>，<code>/bin</code>，<code>/sbin</code>，<code>/usr/X11R6/bin</code>中有定义。<br>所以，只要把这些命令重新取出来就能使用了，也算是个补救的办法。<br><code>export PATH=/usr/bin:/usr/sbin:/bin:/sbin:/usr/X11R6/bin</code><br>转载于:<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/young233/p/10879077.html\">修改profile导致bash不能用的补救方法</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"二、源码编译安装最新稳定版：-1\"><a href=\"#二、源码编译安装最新稳定版：-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、源码编译安装最新稳定版：\"></a>二、源码编译安装最新稳定版：</h2><p><a href=\"http://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.20.1.tar.gz\">nginx1.20.1下载地址：</a><br><a href=\"https://github.com/arut/nginx-dav-ext-module/archive/refs/tags/v3.0.0.tar.gz\">nginx-dav-ext-module v3.0.0下载地址：</a>  </p>\n<h3 id=\"1-卸载并清理安装的nginx\"><a href=\"#1-卸载并清理安装的nginx\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 卸载并清理安装的nginx\"></a>1. 卸载并清理安装的nginx</h3><figure class=\"highlight elixir\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs elixir\">yk<span class=\"hljs-variable\">@yk</span>-<span class=\"hljs-symbol\">pc:</span>~<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$ </span>sudo apt autoremove nginx<br>yk<span class=\"hljs-variable\">@yk</span>-<span class=\"hljs-symbol\">pc:</span>~<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$ </span>sudo apt purge nginx<br>yk<span class=\"hljs-variable\">@yk</span>-<span class=\"hljs-symbol\">pc:</span>~<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$ </span>sudo apt clean<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"2-下载并编译安装\"><a href=\"#2-下载并编译安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 下载并编译安装\"></a>2. 下载并编译安装</h3><figure class=\"highlight gradle\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs gradle\">yk@yk-pc:~<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包$ tar zxvf nginx-<span class=\"hljs-number\">1.21</span>.<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>.tar.gz<br>yk@yk-pc:~<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包$ tar zxvf nginx-dav-ext-module-<span class=\"hljs-number\">3.0</span>.<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>.tar.gz -C <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/home/y</span>k<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包/<br>yk@yk-pc:~<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包$ tar zxvf nginx-<span class=\"hljs-number\">1.21</span>.<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>.tar.gz -C <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/home/y</span>k<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包/<br>yk@yk-pc:~<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包$ cd nginx-<span class=\"hljs-number\">1.21</span>.<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span><br>yk@yk-pc:~<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包$ sudo apt-get install libpcre3 libpcre3-dev zlib1g-dev openssl libssl-dev libxslt-dev libgd-dev libgeoip-dev apache2-utils<br>yk@yk-pc:~<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包/nginx-<span class=\"hljs-number\">1.21</span>.<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>$ su root<br>密码：<br>root@yk-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/home/y</span>k<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/nginx-1.21.0#  ./</span>configure --prefix=<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx --with-http_dav_module --with-http_stub_status_module --with-http_flv_module --with-http_gzip_static_module --with-stream --with-stream=dynamic --with-http_realip_module --with-http_v2_module --with-http_image_filter_module  --with-http_image_filter_module=dynamic --with-http_ssl_module --add-module=<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/home/y</span>k<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包/nginx-dav-ext-module-<span class=\"hljs-number\">3.0</span>.<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span><br>root@yk-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/home/y</span>k<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/下载/</span>压缩包/nginx-<span class=\"hljs-number\">1.21</span>.<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span># make &amp;&amp; make install<br>root@yk-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx#  ln -s <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/sbin/</span>nginx <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/usr/</span>bin/nginx <br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"三、配置webdav模块-1\"><a href=\"#三、配置webdav模块-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、配置webdav模块\"></a>三、配置webdav模块</h2><h3 id=\"（1）配置webdav\"><a href=\"#（1）配置webdav\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（1）配置webdav\"></a>（1）配置webdav</h3><p><code>root@yk-pc:/etc/nginx/conf# vim nginx.conf</code><br>用以下内容替换原内容：<br><figure class=\"highlight pgsql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br><span class=\"line\">81</span><br><span class=\"line\">82</span><br><span class=\"line\">83</span><br><span class=\"line\">84</span><br><span class=\"line\">85</span><br><span class=\"line\">86</span><br><span class=\"line\">87</span><br><span class=\"line\">88</span><br><span class=\"line\">89</span><br><span class=\"line\">90</span><br><span class=\"line\">91</span><br><span class=\"line\">92</span><br><span class=\"line\">93</span><br><span class=\"line\">94</span><br><span class=\"line\">95</span><br><span class=\"line\">96</span><br><span class=\"line\">97</span><br><span class=\"line\">98</span><br><span class=\"line\">99</span><br><span class=\"line\">100</span><br><span class=\"line\">101</span><br><span class=\"line\">102</span><br><span class=\"line\">103</span><br><span class=\"line\">104</span><br><span class=\"line\">105</span><br><span class=\"line\">106</span><br><span class=\"line\">107</span><br><span class=\"line\">108</span><br><span class=\"line\">109</span><br><span class=\"line\">110</span><br><span class=\"line\">111</span><br><span class=\"line\">112</span><br><span class=\"line\">113</span><br><span class=\"line\">114</span><br><span class=\"line\">115</span><br><span class=\"line\">116</span><br><span class=\"line\">117</span><br><span class=\"line\">118</span><br><span class=\"line\">119</span><br><span class=\"line\">120</span><br><span class=\"line\">121</span><br><span class=\"line\">122</span><br><span class=\"line\">123</span><br><span class=\"line\">124</span><br><span class=\"line\">125</span><br><span class=\"line\">126</span><br><span class=\"line\">127</span><br><span class=\"line\">128</span><br><span class=\"line\">129</span><br><span class=\"line\">130</span><br><span class=\"line\">131</span><br><span class=\"line\">132</span><br><span class=\"line\">133</span><br><span class=\"line\">134</span><br><span class=\"line\">135</span><br><span class=\"line\">136</span><br><span class=\"line\">137</span><br><span class=\"line\">138</span><br><span class=\"line\">139</span><br><span class=\"line\">140</span><br><span class=\"line\">141</span><br><span class=\"line\">142</span><br><span class=\"line\">143</span><br><span class=\"line\">144</span><br><span class=\"line\">145</span><br><span class=\"line\">146</span><br><span class=\"line\">147</span><br><span class=\"line\">148</span><br><span class=\"line\">149</span><br><span class=\"line\">150</span><br><span class=\"line\">151</span><br><span class=\"line\">152</span><br><span class=\"line\">153</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs pgsql\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#user  nobody;</span><br>worker_processes  <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>;<br><br><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#error_log  logs/error.log;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#error_log  logs/error.log  notice;</span><br><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#error_log  logs/error.log  info;</span><br><br><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#pid        logs/nginx.pid;</span><br><br><br>events &#123;<br>    worker_connections  <span class=\"hljs-number\">1024</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><br>http &#123;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">include</span>       mime.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">types</span>;<br>    default_type  application/octet-stream;<br><br>    log_format  main  <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;$remote_addr - $remote_user [$time_local] &quot;$request&quot; &#x27;</span><br>                      <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;$status $body_bytes_sent &quot;$http_referer&quot; &#x27;</span><br>                      <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;&quot;$http_user_agent&quot; &quot;$http_x_forwarded_for&quot;&#x27;</span>;<br><br>    access_log  logs/<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">access</span>.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">log</span>  main;<br><br>    sendfile        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">on</span>;<br>    tcp_nopush     <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">on</span>;<br><br>    #keepalive_timeout  <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;<br>    keepalive_timeout  <span class=\"hljs-number\">65</span>;<br><br>    gzip  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">on</span>;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">server</span> &#123;<br>        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">listen</span>       <span class=\"hljs-number\">80</span>;<br>        server_name  localhost;<br>        <br>        #charset koi8-r;<br><br>        access_log  logs/host.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">access</span>.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">log</span>  main;<br><br>        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">location</span> / &#123;<br>            root   html;<br>            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">index</span>  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">index</span>.html <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">index</span>.htm;<br>        &#125;<br><br>        error_page  <span class=\"hljs-number\">404</span>              /<span class=\"hljs-number\">404.</span>html;<br><br>        # redirect <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">server</span> error pages <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">to</span> the static page /<span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>x.html<br>        #<br>       error_page   <span class=\"hljs-number\">500</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">502</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">503</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">504</span>  /<span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>x.html;<br>        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">location</span> = /<span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>x.html &#123;<br>            root   html;<br>        &#125;<br><br>        # proxy the PHP scripts <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">to</span> Apache listening <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">on</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">127.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.1</span>:<span class=\"hljs-number\">80</span><br>        #<br>        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">location</span> ~ \\.php$ &#123;<br>            proxy_pass   http://<span class=\"hljs-number\">127.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.1</span>;<br>        &#125;<br><br>        # pass the PHP scripts <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">to</span> FastCGI <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">server</span> listening <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">on</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">127.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.1</span>:<span class=\"hljs-number\">9000</span><br>        #<br>        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">location</span> ~ \\.php$ &#123;<br>            root           html;<br>            fastcgi_pass   <span class=\"hljs-number\">127.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.1</span>:<span class=\"hljs-number\">9000</span>;<br>            fastcgi_index  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">index</span>.php;<br>            fastcgi_param  SCRIPT_FILENAME  /scripts$fastcgi_script_name;<br>            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">include</span>        fastcgi_params;<br>        &#125;<br><br>        # deny <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">access</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">to</span> .htaccess files, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> Apach<span class=\"hljs-string\">e&#x27;s document root</span><br><span class=\"hljs-string\">        # concurs with nginx&#x27;</span>s one<br>        #<br>        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">location</span> ~ /\\.ht &#123;<br>            deny  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">all</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br><br><br>    # another virtual host <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">using</span> mix <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">of</span> IP-, <span class=\"hljs-type\">name</span>-, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">and</span> port-based <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">configuration</span><br>    #<br>    #<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">server</span> &#123;<br>    #    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">listen</span>       <span class=\"hljs-number\">8000</span>;<br>    #    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">listen</span>       somename:<span class=\"hljs-number\">8080</span>;<br>    #    server_name  somename  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">alias</span>  another.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">alias</span>;<br><br>    #    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">location</span> / &#123;<br>    #        root   html;<br>    #        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">index</span>  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">index</span>.html <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">index</span>.htm;<br>    #    &#125;<br>    #&#125;<br><br>      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">server</span>&#123;<br>          <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">listen</span>    <span class=\"hljs-number\">81</span>;<br>          server_name webdav;<br>          error_log /etc/nginx/logs/webdav.error.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">log</span> error;<br>          access_log  /etc/nginx/logs/webdav.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">access</span>.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">log</span> combined;<br>       <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">location</span> / &#123;<br>             root /home/yk/www/nginx/webdav;<br>             charset utf<span class=\"hljs-number\">-8</span>;<br>             autoindex <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">on</span>;<br>             dav_methods  PUT <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">DELETE</span> MKCOL <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">COPY</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">MOVE</span>;<br>             dav_ext_methods PROPFIND <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">OPTIONS</span>;<br>             create_full_put_path <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">on</span>;<br>             dav_access <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">user</span>:rw <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">group</span>:r <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">all</span>:r;<br>             auth_basic &quot;Authorized Users Only&quot;;<br>             auth_basic_user_file /etc/nginx/.htpasswd;<br>             client_max_body_size <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>G;<br>                &#125;<br>           error_page   <span class=\"hljs-number\">500</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">502</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">503</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">504</span>  /<span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>x.html;<br>           <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">location</span> = /<span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>x.html &#123;<br>               root   /etc/nginx/html;<br>             &#125;<br>        &#125;<br><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">server</span> &#123;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">listen</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">8080</span>;<br>    error_log /etc/nginx/logs/jianguoyun.error.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">log</span> error;<br>    access_log  /etc/nginx/logs/jianguoyun.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">access</span>.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">log</span> combined;<br> <br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">location</span> / &#123;<br>        root /home/yk/www/nginx/jianguoyun;<br>        autoindex <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">on</span>;<br>        dav_methods PUT <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">DELETE</span> MKCOL <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">COPY</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">MOVE</span>;<br>        dav_ext_methods PROPFIND <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">OPTIONS</span>;<br>        create_full_put_path <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">on</span>;<br>        dav_access <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">user</span>:rw <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">group</span>:r <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">all</span>:r;<br>        auth_basic &quot;Authorized Users Only&quot;;<br>        auth_basic_user_file /etc/nginx/.htpasswd;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br>    # HTTPS <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">server</span><br>    #<br>    #<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">server</span> &#123;<br>    #    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">listen</span>       <span class=\"hljs-number\">443</span> ssl;<br>    #    server_name  localhost;<br><br>    #    ssl_certificate      cert.pem;<br>    #    ssl_certificate_key  cert.key;<br><br>    #    ssl_session_cache    shared:SSL:<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>m;<br>    #    ssl_session_timeout  <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>m;<br><br>    #    ssl_ciphers  HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5;<br>    #    ssl_prefer_server_ciphers  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">on</span>;<br><br>    #    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">location</span> / &#123;<br>    #        root   html;<br>    #        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">index</span>  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">index</span>.html <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">index</span>.htm;<br>    #    &#125;<br>    #&#125;<br><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"（2）设置webdav帐号和密码：\"><a href=\"#（2）设置webdav帐号和密码：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（2）设置webdav帐号和密码：\"></a>（2）设置webdav帐号和密码：</h3><figure class=\"highlight awk\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs awk\">root@yk-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># echo -n &#x27;yk:&#x27; | tee /etc/nginx/.htpasswd</span><br>yk:root@yk-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># openssl passwd -apr1 | tee -a /etc/nginx/.htpasswd</span><br>Password: <br>Verifying - Password: <br><span class=\"hljs-variable\">$apr1</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">$6aLRK</span>.<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>F<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$gg76W8E9vT65vn1cE</span>/Mk41<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"（3）挂载到坚果云方法\"><a href=\"#（3）挂载到坚果云方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（3）挂载到坚果云方法\"></a>（3）挂载到坚果云方法</h3><figure class=\"highlight awk\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs awk\">yk@yk-pc:~$ sudo apt-get install davfs2<br>yk@yk-pc:~$ mkdir -p <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/home/y</span>k<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/www/</span>nginx/jianguoyun<br>yk@yk-pc:~$ sudo vim  <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>davfs2/davfs2.conf<br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#ignore_dav_header 0</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>  改为：<br><code>ignore_dav_header 1</code><br>  挂载：<br><code>yk@yk-pc:~$ sudo mount -t davfs https://dav.jianguoyun.com/dav/ /home/yk/www/nginx/jianguoyun</code><br>取消挂载：<br><code>yk@yk-pc:~$ sudo fusermount -u /home/yk/www/nginx/jianguoyun</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"（4）nginx加入到systemctl服务运行\"><a href=\"#（4）nginx加入到systemctl服务运行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（4）nginx加入到systemctl服务运行\"></a>（4）<code>nginx</code>加入到<code>systemctl</code>服务运行</h3><p>  <code>yk@yk-pc:~$ sudo vim /usr/lib/systemd/system/nginx.service</code><br>输入以下内容并保存<br><figure class=\"highlight ini\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs ini\"><span class=\"hljs-section\">[Unit]</span><br><span class=\"hljs-attr\">Description</span>=nginx<br><span class=\"hljs-attr\">After</span>=network.target<br><span class=\"hljs-section\">[Service]</span><br><span class=\"hljs-attr\">Type</span>=forking<br><span class=\"hljs-attr\">PIDFile</span>=/etc/nginx/logs/nginx.pid<br><span class=\"hljs-attr\">ExecStart</span>=/etc/nginx/sbin/nginx<br><span class=\"hljs-attr\">ExecReload</span>=/etc/nginx/sbin/nginx -s reload<br><span class=\"hljs-attr\">ExecStop</span>=/etc/nginx/sbin/nginx -s stop<br><span class=\"hljs-attr\">PrivateTmp</span>=<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span><br><span class=\"hljs-section\">[Install]</span><br><span class=\"hljs-attr\">WantedBy</span>=multi-user.target<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"（5）常用命令：\"><a href=\"#（5）常用命令：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（5）常用命令：\"></a>（5）常用命令：</h3><figure class=\"highlight elixir\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs elixir\">yk<span class=\"hljs-variable\">@yk</span>-<span class=\"hljs-symbol\">pc:</span>~<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$ </span>systemctl daemon-reload<br>yk<span class=\"hljs-variable\">@yk</span>-<span class=\"hljs-symbol\">pc:</span>~<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$ </span>systemctl start/stop/reload nginx<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"四、手机用的连接为webdav软件：-1\"><a href=\"#四、手机用的连接为webdav软件：-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、手机用的连接为webdav软件：\"></a>四、手机用的连接为webdav软件：</h2><p>   <strong>苹果：FE文件管理器、ES文件浏览器</strong><br>   <strong>安卓：CX文件管理器、ES文件浏览器</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"五、一些问题及解决方法：\"><a href=\"#五、一些问题及解决方法：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、一些问题及解决方法：\"></a>五、一些问题及解决方法：</h2><h3 id=\"1-查找进程：\"><a href=\"#1-查找进程：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 查找进程：\"></a>1. 查找进程：</h3><p>  查询端口：<br>  <code>ps -ef |grep nginx</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-开放端口：\"><a href=\"#2-开放端口：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 开放端口：\"></a>2. 开放端口：</h3><figure class=\"highlight typescript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs typescript\">yk<span class=\"hljs-meta\">@yk</span>-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/logs$ sudo apt-get install iptables<br>yk<span class=\"hljs-meta\">@yk</span>-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/logs$ sudo ln -s /usr/sbin/iptables /usr/bin/iptables  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//建立软连接</span><br>yk<span class=\"hljs-meta\">@yk</span>-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/logs$ sudo iptables -I INPUT -p tcp --dport <span class=\"hljs-number\">81</span> -j ACCEPT  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//开放81端口</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>持久化规则：这里我们需要在安装一下工具来帮我们实现，这里我们使用 <code>iptables-persistent</code><br>安装<code>iptables-persistent</code><br>  <code>yk@yk-pc:/etc/nginx/logs$ sudo apt-get install iptables-persistent</code><br>持久化规则<br><figure class=\"highlight typescript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs typescript\">yk<span class=\"hljs-meta\">@yk</span>-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/logs$ sudo netfilter-persistent save<br>yk<span class=\"hljs-meta\">@yk</span>-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/logs$ sudo netfilter-persistent reload<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><br>完成上述操作就可以永久打开我们需要的端口了</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-关于权限问题：\"><a href=\"#3-关于权限问题：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 关于权限问题：\"></a>3. 关于权限问题：</h3><figure class=\"highlight awk\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs awk\"> yk@yk-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/conf$ sudo vim nginx.conf<br> [sudo] yk 的密码：<br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#user  nobody;</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注释掉<code>user</code>，改为<br><code>user  nginx;</code><br>重新加载出现：错误提示如下：<br><figure class=\"highlight awk\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs awk\">yk@yk-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/conf$ sudo nginx -s reload<br>nginx: [emerg] getpwnam(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;nginx&quot;</span>) failed <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/conf/</span>nginx.conf:<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span><br>yk@yk-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/conf$ sudo nginx -s closed<br>nginx: invalid option: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;-s closed&quot;</span><br>yk@yk-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/conf$ sudo nginx -s stop<br>nginx: [emerg] getpwnam(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;nginx&quot;</span>) failed <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/conf/</span>nginx.conf:<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><br><strong>解决办法：</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight typescript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs typescript\">yk<span class=\"hljs-meta\">@yk</span>-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/conf$ sudo useradd -s /sbin/nologin -M  nginx<br>useradd：用户“nginx”已存在<br>yk<span class=\"hljs-meta\">@yk</span>-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/conf$ id nginx<br>uid=<span class=\"hljs-number\">117</span>(nginx) gid=<span class=\"hljs-number\">125</span>(nginx) 组=<span class=\"hljs-number\">125</span>(nginx)<br>yk<span class=\"hljs-meta\">@yk</span>-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/conf$ systemctl start nginx<br>yk<span class=\"hljs-meta\">@yk</span>-pc:<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>nginx/conf$  sudo nginx -s reload<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"4-make-upgrade-平滑升级\"><a href=\"#4-make-upgrade-平滑升级\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. make upgrade 平滑升级\"></a>4. <code>make upgrade</code> 平滑升级</h3><figure class=\"highlight awk\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs awk\"><span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/sbin/m</span>ount.davfs: mounting failed; the server does not support WebDAV<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>原因是<code>mount.davfs</code>命令在挂载时和 <code>WebDAV</code> 服务器建立连接，并通过 <code>libneon</code>库的 <code>ne_options</code> 函数发送 <code>HTTP OPTIONS</code> 请求获取 <code>WebDAV</code> 服务器能力，虽然返回成功但判断坚果云 <code>WebDAV</code> 服务器不支持 <code>Class 1 WebDAV</code>，因此直接报错挂载失败。<br>看到这里解决办法也就简单了，<code>davfs2</code> 提供了通过配置文件禁用 <code>WebDAV</code>头检测的功能，<br><figure class=\"highlight awk\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs awk\">直接修改 <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/etc/</span>davfs2/davfs2.conf 配置文件解注释并改为：ignore_dav_header <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"参考：\"><a href=\"#参考：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考：\"></a>参考：</h2><ol>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.v5b7.com/webserver/nginx/nginx_webdav.html\">nginx配置webdav：</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/catlee/p/10290497.html\">源码编译安装nginx详细步骤：</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://xieshaohu.wordpress.com/2019/07/12/nginx%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85webdav%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97/\">nginx编译安装webdav模块：</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.ghostry.cn/server/889.html\">debian下为Nginx添加webdav:</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u013401853/article/details/113094734\">davfs挂载与使用缺陷：</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.moerats.com/archives/317/\">Linux通过安装davfs2来挂载webdav网盘：</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/Dev0ps/p/12000221.html\">Nginx服务加到systemctl:</a></li>\n</ol>\n",
            "tags": [
                "webdav"
            ]
        }
    ]
}